\v 1 mm  
\s1 Man sar kitsip bu vuna vienviendon  
\m \k Bu muomuo simi vona rengeir\k*  
\li1 \it Mi sinavien bu muomuo -\it* Aposol 6:1–6; 14:23 † 1 Timote 3:1–13 † Tito 1:5–9.  
\li1 \it Mi saran mi tsientsang sibu muomuo -\it* Mataio 28:18–20 † Luka 22:24–27 † Aposol 20:17–35 † 1 Tesalonika 2:1–12 † 1 Timote 4:1–16 † 2 Timote 2:1–26, 3:10–17, 4:1–5 † Tito 2:7–8 † 1 Petro 5:1–4.  
\li1 \it Magi minangarei bu muomuo -\it* 1 Korinto 9:14 † Galatia 6:6 † 1 Tesalonika 5:12–13 † 1 Timote 5:17–22 † Iburu 13:7; 13:17.  
\m \k Bu natuon e Raban\k*  
\li1 Ioanes 1:12–13 † Roma 8:14–17 † Galatia 4:6–7 † Iburu 12:5–11 † 1 Ioanes 3:1–3.  
\m \k Bu tienebeir ni varam nge vinavinar\k*  
\li1 Mataio 9:13 † Marko 12:33 † Roma 12:1 † Iburu 9:6–10:18.  
\m \k E Iesu Karisito\k*  
\li1 \it E Iesu Karisito eie e Natuon e Raban -\it* Mataio 11:27–30; 16:13–17 † Luka 1:35 † Ioanes 1:1–18; 5:19–29; 6:35–40; 8:58; 11:25–27; 14:5–11; 17:1–5; 20:26–31 † Aposol 3:13–16; 4:10–12 † Roma 1:3–4 † 1 Korinto 3:11 † 2 Korinto 4:4–6; 5:21 † Galatia 4:4–5 † Pilippoi 2:5–11 † Kolose 1:15–20; 2:9–10 † Iburu 1:1–14; 7:26–28 † 1 Ioanes 2:1–2; 5:20 † Puek Vasangan 1:12–18; 19:11–16.  
\li1 \it E Natuon e Raban a nga tsourbeit ka -\it* Ioanes 1:14 † Luka 1:26–38 † Mataio 1:18–25 † Luka 2:1–20 † Mataio 2:1–23 † Galatia 4:4–5 † Pilippoi 2:6–7 † Iburu 2:14–18.  
\li1 \it E Iesu a nga vavasengei simi kulou nge vatoa bu tamat mienarouk -\it* Mataio 4:23–25; 7:28–29; 9:35–36; 11:1–6 † Luka 4:14–44 † Aposol 10:36–38, Ioanes 20:30–31.  
\li1 \it E Iesu a nga tsana palan bu kepineits ni vovokudier -\it* Mataio 8:1–4; 8:5–13; 8:14–15; 8:23–27; 8:28–33; 9:1–7; 9:18–26; 9:27–31; 9:32–33; 12:9–14; 12:22; 14:15–21; 14:22–32; 15:22–28; 15:32–38; 17:14–18; 20:29–34; 21:18–22 † Marko 1:21–28; 7:32–37; 8:22–25 † Luka 5:4–8; 7:11–15; 13:10–13; 14:1–4; 17:12–14; 22:50–51 † Ioanes 2:1–11; 4:46–54; 5:5–9; 9:1–7; 11:11–44; 21:4–6 † Aposol 2:22.  
\li1 \it Bu muomuo gi nga rakopie e Iesu nge terie simi miensei -\it* Mataio 26:47–68; 27:1–2; 27:11–31 † Marko 14:43–65; 15:1–20 † Luka 22:47–53; 22:63–71; 23:1–25 † Ioanes 18:1–14; 18:19–24; 18:28–19:16.  
\li1 \it Gi nga vetekiuo e Iesu simi koitskoits -\it* Mataio 27:32–56 † Marko 15:21–41 † Luka 23:26–49 † Ioanes 19:17–37.  
\li1 \it Gi nga puonongie e Iesu -\it* Mataio 27:57–66 † Marko 15:42–47 † Luka 23:50–56 † Ioanes 19:38–42.  
\li1 \it E Iesu a nga to muerngei simi miensei ma bu mei gi nga dengarie -\it* Mataio 28:1–20 † Marko 16:1–8 † Luka 24:1–49 † Ioanes 20:1–21:14 † Aposol 1:3–8; 2:24–32; 3:15; 4:10; 4:33; 10:39–43; 13:29–39; 17:2–3; 17:30–31 † Roma 1:4; 4:24–25 † 1 Korinto 15:3–8; 15:12–21 † Puek Vasangan 1:18.  
\li1 \it E Iesu a nga kien i kur simi rangit -\it* Luka 24:50–51 † Aposol 1:9–11; 2:32–36; 5:30–31 † Roma 8:34 † Epeso 1:20–23 † Pilippoi 2:9–11 † Iburu 1:3–11; 2:9; 4:14–16; 7:25–26; 10:12–14 † 1 Petro 3:22.  
\li1 \it E Iesu ta ba muer peuk i keim -\it* Mataio 24:29–44 † Ioanes 14:1–3 † Aposol 1:10–11; 3:19–21 † Pilippoi 3:20–21 † Kolose 3:4 † 1 Tesalonika 1:9–10; 3:13; 4:13–5:11 † 2 Tesalonika 1:6–10; 2:1–4 † 1 Timote 6:13–15 † 2 Timote 4:8 † Iburu 9:28 † 2 Petro 3:1–18 † 1 Ioanes 3:1–3 † Puek Vasangan 1:7; 22:12–13.  
